description: This package contains full set of binaries for the Visual Studio Test Platform (vstest). vstest provides a modern, cross platform testing engine that also powers the testing on .NET Core. Supports the following popular test frameworks - MSTest(v1 and v2), xUnit and Nunit with support for extensibility. Visit https://github.com/microsoft/vstest to know more about vstest platform.
